 (i)  the form and manner in which any application, claim, return or information may be made or furnished
and the fees that may be levied in respect of any application or claim;
(j)  the manner in which any document required to be filed under this Act may be verified;
(k)  the procedure to be followed on applications for refunds;
(kk) the procedure to be followed in calculating interest payable by assessees or interest payable by
Government to assessees under any provision of this Act, including the rounding off of the period for
